<h2>Why Pinterest Outperforms Other Platforms for Traffic</h2>
<p>Most social platforms keep users on the platform. Pinterest sends them to your website. Every Pin includes a clickable link. No "link in bio" workaround needed.</p>
<h3>Pinterest vs Instagram for Business</h3>
