<p>The content lifespan difference alone makes Pinterest the strongest compounding traffic platform. A Pin published today can generate clicks 6 months from now. An Instagram post published today generates most of its engagement within 6 hours.</p>
<h3>The Unbranded Search Advantage</h3>
<p>97% of Pinterest searches do not include a brand name. Users search "minimalist living room ideas" not "IKEA living room." Your content competes on relevance, not brand recognition. A small business with excellent Pins outranks a Fortune 500 company that does not optimize for Pinterest search.</p>
<p>85% of weekly Pinterest users have made a purchase based on Pins they saw, per <a href="https://www.demandsage.com/pinterest-statistics/">DemandSage</a>. The platform combines search intent with purchase intent. No other social platform does both at this scale.</p>
