<h2>How Pinterest SEO Works</h2>
<p>Pinterest is a search engine. SEO fundamentals (keyword research, placement, and optimization) apply directly. The businesses that treat Pinterest like a search engine outperform those who treat it like a social feed.</p>
<h3>Where to Place Keywords</h3>
