- <strong>File name:</strong> <code>minimalist-living-room-small-space-ideas.jpg</code></p>
<h3>Rich Pins</h3>
<p>Rich Pins pull metadata directly from your website and display it on the Pin. They increase trust and <a href="/blog/organic-ctr-by-position/">click-through rates</a>.</p>
